  allLines:
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Damn, they\u2019re both such hotties. I sometimes wish I was a mere
      counselor than a higher up. Then I\u2019d get to hang with both of these bombshells."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Well, wanna swap for the day?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: F*** no!
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 2
    characterName: Counselor
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Oh, uh. Okay then.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Loreen
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 146a6ce1894c7084984f7771ba7e263e, type: 3}
    sentence: So, a lawyer, huh? A lawyer that drinks, nonetheless. Are you one of
      those shitty ones or do you have dignity?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ece41423a199ba04f8804d355c231cbb, type: 3}
    sentence: "Wow, so direct. You know, I tend to get mostly respectable clients
      but of course I have to defend the scum of the earth from time to time too.
      They\u2019re mostly the ones that pay for my rent so, can\u2019t really complain."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Loreen
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I didn\u2019t mean to sound that judgemental. I serve my fair share
      of that same scum most often than not."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: You pour their drinks, I cover up their secrets. Oh to be an interplanetary
      piggy and live a life so glamorous.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Loreen
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: You think their lives are glamorous?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "\u2018Course not. I bet I know more about their dirty secrets than
      you do. A drunk man is an honest man, a desperate man however, is willing to
      give so much more than honesty."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Loreen
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 
    eventTrigger: 
    choices:
    - choices: Collecting dirty secrets is one of my many specialties.
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3464f9ea9ea96d84fb3c991a79fb0808, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0
      heartReward: 0
    - choices: Best not to get drunk around you then.
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0f35e0cadebd46f46a7306ab6264ebbe, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0.5
      heartReward: 0
    - choices: You seem to get a rise out of that.
